  "id": "RAW_7e2a8e20",
  "title": "GLM-ASR 开源，智谱 AI 输入法发布",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzI3NzQ0Mg==&mid=2247492407&idx=1&sn=ddf30daa1e30f788e40b9e44449e6bf1",
  "date": "2025-12-10 01:01:00",
  "author": "智谱",
  "siteName": "智谱",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img data-imgfileid=\"100008745\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.43666666666666665\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1800\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/UBWAWibiaa4jeNZXo8lmagjDJVYCHsr5VibY1tgdecEBV4K1eeOaedNjOOnc9VtFmnDp6OUKhBEXgueU2bGSRpCCQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"253\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"252\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251211231142_bb9fcb6a\" style=\"background-color:transparent;border-radius:6px;max-width:100%;display:inline-block;width:100%;font-size:medium;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;text-align:center;\"><span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">今天，我们正式发布并开源</span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">GLM-ASR系列语音识别模型</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，并推出基于该系列模型打造的桌面端</span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">智谱AI输入法</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">本次发布模型与</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">产品包</span><span leaf=\"\">括：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:20px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:34px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">GLM-ASR-2512</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">：全球领先的云端语音识别模型；</span></span></li>\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">GLM-ASR-Nano-2512</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">：参数量仅</span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">1.5B</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">的开源SOTA端侧语音模型；</span></span></li>\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">智谱AI输入法</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">：将语音识别与大模型深度融合的桌面端效率工具。</span></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">我们希望让用户真正做到“</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">动动嘴，活就干了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">”，从“把话变成字”走向“直接用语音完成任务”。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;font-size: 20px;padding-bottom: 12px;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM-ASR系列模型</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">开源</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">GLM-ASR-2512</span></span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">是智谱新一代语音识别模型，支持将语音实时转换为文字。在多场景、多语种、多口音的真实复杂环境测试中，保持行业领先的识别表现，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">字符错误率（CER）仅为</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">0.0717</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在此基础上，我们开源了</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">GLM-ASR-Nano-2512</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">。</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">这</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">是一个</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">1.5B参数</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">的端侧模型，却取得了当前开源语音识别方向的</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">SOTA表现</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">，并在部分测试中优于若干闭源模型。它将识别能力压缩到本地运</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">行，在保证高精度的同时，实现</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">更强的隐私保护与更低的交互延迟</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:0px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miymbgqy17ox\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100008743\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6435185185185185\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 6px;background-color: transparent;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"576\" data-backh=\"371\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20251211231142_55d49ec9\"></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">基于上述模型能力，我们</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">正式上线</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">智谱</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">AI</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">输入法</span>，让用户在</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">PC</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">端</span>用语音</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">丝滑</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">交互。用户不但可以实现精准的语音转文字，还可以实现翻译、改写等</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">智能</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">操作，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">真正实现“指尖即模型，语音即指令”</span>。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;font-size: 20px;padding-bottom: 12px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">智谱AI输入法：在输入中直接调起模型能力</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">智谱AI输入法基于GLM-ASR系列模型打造，让用户在电脑端用语音丝滑交互。用户不仅可以实现精准的语音转文字，还可以在输入法中直接调用大模型能力，完成翻译、改写、情绪转化等操作，实现“指尖即模型，语音即指令”。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:20px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:34px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">所选即所改，从听写到改写的一体化</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">传统输入法只负责打字，而智谱AI输入法直接调用底层GLM模型帮助用户翻译、扩写、精简屏幕上的任意一段文字，同时完成智能润色，让输出更加自然、通顺。整个过程在输入框内完成，实现“</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">理解-执行-替换</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">”一体化，无需在多个应用间反复切换。</span></span></span></li>\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">千人千面人设切换</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">：支持设置不同“人设”风格，实现同一句话在不同场景下的不同表达。例如，在工作场景中，选择“面对老板”，口语化的碎碎念瞬间转化为逻辑严谨、条理清晰的工作汇报；在生活场景中，切换至“面对伴侣”，文字则变得温柔俏皮，贴近日常聊天语境。</span></span></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:20px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:34px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">Vibe Coding（语感编程）</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">搭子</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">：针对开发者，我们特别推出了Vibe Coding体验，并与智谱Coding Plan账号打通。结合多语言支持与代码理解能力，开发者可以通过语音快速输入代码逻辑和注释、查找遗忘的Linux指令、用自然语言指挥AI完成复杂数学计算或脚本编写</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">。同样，设计师也可以从传统的“用手抠图”过渡到“用嘴做设计”。</span></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:20px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:34px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">耳语捕捉与高效热词</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">：针对开放式办公室、图书馆等公共场景，我们优化了对微弱声音的捕捉能力，并区分环境噪声。只需轻声说话，即可精准转为文字，解决公共场合“不好意思用语音输入”的痛点。同时，支持用户一键导入</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">专属词汇、项目代号</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">（如AutoGLM）及生僻人名、地名等。只需在设置中添加一次。</span></span></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <h3 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;font-size: 20px;padding-bottom: 12px;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验与下载</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">现在</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">，你</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">可以在<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">智谱</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">开放</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">平台</span>bigmodel.cn调用最新</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">GLM-ASR-2512</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">模型。</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">同时，</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">我们为<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">开源社区</span>提供了1.5B的端侧模型GLM-ASR-Nano-2512，权重及推理代码</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">均</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">已发布。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">即日起，</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">智谱AI输入法</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">面向</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">所有用户</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">开放</span></span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">，</span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">并免费</span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">提供</span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">2000</span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">积分</span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">，相当于</span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">28天使用时长</span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">。欢迎体验！</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:20px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:34px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM-ASR-2512</span></span></li>\n   <ul style=\"padding-left:24px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;margin-top:0px;line-height:30px;margin-bottom:10px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">使用指南</span>：</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n       <br> \n      </span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://docs.bigmodel.cn/cn/guide/models/sound-and-video/glm-asr-2512\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.bigmodel.cn/cn/guide/models/sound-and-video/glm-asr-2512</a></span></span></li>\n    <li style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">体验中心</span>：</span></span>\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://bigmodel.cn/trialcenter/modeltrial/voice\" target=\"_blank\">https://bigmodel.cn/trialcenter/modeltrial/voice</a></span></p></li>\n    <li style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">接口文档</span>：</span></span>\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://</span><span leaf=\"\">d</span><span leaf=\"\">ocs.bigmodel.cn/api-reference/</span><span leaf=\"\">模型-api/语音转文本</span></p></li>\n   </ul>\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM-ASR-Nano-2512</span></span></li>\n   <ul style=\"padding-left:24px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;margin-top:0px;line-height:30px;margin-bottom:10px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">Hugging Face</span></span><span leaf=\"\">：</span></span>\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/zai-org/GLM-ASR-Nano-2512\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/zai-org/GLM-ASR-Nano-2512</a></span></p></li>\n    <li style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">魔搭社区</span></span><span leaf=\"\">：</span></span>\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.modelscope.cn/models/ZhipuAI/GLM-ASR-Nano-2512\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.modelscope.cn/models/ZhipuAI/GLM-ASR-Nano-2512</a></span></p></li>\n   </ul>\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">智谱AI输入法</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">：</span></span></li>\n   <ul style=\"padding-left:24px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;margin-top:0px;line-height:30px;margin-bottom:10px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">Mac/Win</span>访问下载：</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://autoglm.zhipuai.cn/autotyper/\" target=\"_blank\">https://autoglm.zhipuai.cn/autotyper/</a></span></span></li>\n   </ul>\n  </ul>\n  <p></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "智谱 AI 开源 GLM-ASR 系列语音识别模型，包括高性能云端模型和 SOTA 端侧模型，并发布基于这些模型打造的桌面端智谱 AI 输入法，旨在通过语音实现智能高效任务处理。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "智谱 AI 开源 GLM-ASR 系列语音识别模型，包括高性能云端模型和 SOTA 端侧模型，并发布基于这些模型打造的桌面端智谱 AI 输入法，旨在通过语音实现智能高效任务处理。",
  "summary": "智谱 AI 正式发布并开源了 GLM-ASR 系列语音识别模型，其中包括全球领先的云端模型 GLM-ASR-2512 和参数量仅 1.5B 但表现优异的开源 SOTA 端侧模型 GLM-ASR-Nano-2512。同时，智谱 AI 推出了基于这些模型开发的桌面端效率工具——智谱 AI 输入法。该输入法不仅支持精准的语音转文字，还深度融合大模型能力，实现了翻译、改写、情绪转化、代码生成等多种智能操作，旨在让用户通过语音指令直接完成复杂任务，大幅提升 PC 端交互效率和体验。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "GLM-ASR 系列模型实现了语音识别的 SOTA 表现，兼顾云端与端侧需求。",
